        line-height: 2em; font-family: inherit; vertical-align:
        baseline; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.25em;
        text-transform: uppercase;" class=""><span style="box-sizing: border-box;
          margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit;
          vertical-align: baseline; text-align: left;" class=""><a href="http://semi-legitimate.com/blog/index.html" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;
