              font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:
              inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;
              vertical-align: baseline;" class="">BLOG:<span class="">&nbsp;</span></em></a><span id="blog-title" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">HOW TO REWRITE OUTGOING ADDRESS IN POSTFIX</span></span></h2>
    </header>
    <div class="pos-content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;
      padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal;
      font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal;
      font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit;
      font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px;
      line-height: inherit; font-family: Lato, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(162, 162, 162);
      letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start;
      text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal;
      widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;
      background-color: rgb(31, 30, 33); text-decoration-style: initial;
      text-decoration-color: initial;">
      <div class="element-textarea first element last" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;
        border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;
          border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class=""><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">Sometimes I find myself configuring an internal
            Linux machine to be able to send emails for alerts or from a
            particular application. Since this will not be a primary
            mail server, I just want to rewrite the outgoing address to
            be something that make sense with the proper domain for the
            users. Here are the quick steps to accomplish this:</p>
        </div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;
          border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">
          <pre class="bash" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: inherit; font-family: monospace; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;
<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(194, 12, 185);" class="">vi</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>etc<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>postfix<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>main.cf
&nbsp;</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">Modify the "mydomain" variable to your email
            domain</p>
          <pre class="bash" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: inherit; font-family: monospace; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;
mydomain = <a href="http://example.com" class="">example.com</a>
&nbsp;</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">Make sure to uncomment the proper network
            interface. I'm usually lazy and just do all.</p>
          <pre class="bash" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: inherit; font-family: monospace; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;
inet_interfaces = all
&nbsp;</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">Now at the bottom of this file you need to
            specify the generic map file for rewriting the address.</p>
          <pre class="bash" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: inherit; font-family: monospace; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;
smtp_generic_maps = hash:<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>etc<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>postfix<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>generic
&nbsp;</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">Save and exit main.cf. Now we need to edit
            /etc/postfix/generic</p>
          <pre class="bash" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: inherit; font-family: monospace; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;
<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(194, 12, 185);" class="">vi</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>etc<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>postfix<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>generic
&nbsp;</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">You need to specify the mapping of the original
            address to the one you want. Since in this case I just want
            to rewrite everything I usually add the following two lines
            and it seems to catch everything.</p>
          <pre class="bash" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: inherit; font-family: monospace; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;
 root<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">@</span><a href="http://example.com" class="">example.com</a>   no-reply<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">@</span><a href="http://example.com" class="">example.com</a>
 <span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">@</span><a href="http://example.com" class="">example.com</a>       no-reply<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">@</span><a href="http://example.com" class="">example.com</a>
&nbsp;</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">Save and exit the file. Now we need to create the
            postfix db.</p>
          <pre class="bash" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: inherit; font-family: monospace; vertical-align: baseline;">&nbsp;
postmap <span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>etc<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>postfix<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;" class="">/</span>generic
&nbsp;</pre><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 2em;
            padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align:
            baseline;" class="">This will create the /etc/postfix/generic.db hash
            file.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

